Notes: SP's Groshek scored 15 of her 19 points in first half and became 11th player
in school history to score 1,000 career points...SP jumped out to 9-0 lead and
has not trailed in any of its six games...SP now 6-0 for second straight
season...SP led by as many as 35 points in second half.
Game.Officials: Tom Kissinger,  Dennis Inderdahl,  Wesley Porter
